{"tid":1562602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"綠卡同跳閘 全部都咪撚用","createTime":"2019-09-12T05:24:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T08:47:06.000Z","uid":252257,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf78d2b814f4033c70f6487408437c5b0aa6789c","tid":1562602,"uid":252257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:24:02.000Z","msg":"綠卡費用: 用咗一個月綠卡 入咗一舊 用咗2個月<br />\n跳閘費用 : 零 <br />\n<br />\n綠卡感覺: 幾爽<br />\n跳閘感覺: 跳嗰下 好撚爽 我以為個世界係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但跳完落月台急急腳 係咁望番轉頭 好驚有人跟住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n起初以為跳閘冇事 但見到咁多post都係講被人捉 <br />\n就用咗第二個方法 <br />\n爆閘 一鳩用啲力 嗰碌野會縮  <br />\n但我發覺 有啲站未必得  荔枝角,康城,炮台山<br />\n最撚容易都係彩虹同黃大仙 <br />\n手足好心你地細力啲啦 林奠會心痛 <br />\n<br />\n以上純粹個人心得 勿屌"},{"pid":"f67c1abfd883139fe22d8046a433e3d60daa194b","tid":1562602,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:24:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"9a77d366c1f08417c2015ae0d1992585eb9a457d","tid":1562602,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T05:26:51.000Z","msg":"比人捉係因為自己危機意識不足，唔識隨機應變，咁廢點同popo鬥呀"},{"pid":"b9e5fa9a3e54e8b515bcd0d0040395fd70ecbde6","tid":1562602,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:44:40.000Z","msg":"見到有幾個人企係度望住都照入就點都捉啦<br />\n就算係以前都會捉你<br />\n但唔係查飛果班真係班鬼你咩"},{"pid":"90ba17165f8d3eca82237ed34135426701bfddc6","tid":1562602,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}